# Base URL of the deployed backend API.
# In local development this is NOT needed — Vite proxies /api → http://localhost:5001.
# On Vercel (production), set this to your actual backend URL:
#
# Example (Render):  https://expenseflow-api.onrender.com/api
# Example (Railway): https://expenseflow-api.up.railway.app/api
VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-url.com/api
